                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-121-off679 t18240114-121-crimeloc682"></join>. On the 6th of January, about twelve o'clock, I put two loins of mutton on the stall board; somebody ran in, and said three boys had taken some - I ran out, and kept my eye on three boys, of whom the prisoner was the foremost; he looked back, and saw me, and on my getting near him, I saw him drop the mutton. I called Stop thief! Taylor ran out, and stopped him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240114-121-person1112">
                  JAMES 
                  TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t18240114-121-person1112" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
