                     <interp inst="t18240114-121-person1112" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I heard a cry, ran out, and saw Robinson's man stop the prisoner. I collared him; Robinson came up with the mutton, and said he could swear to him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. When the man took me, he said,</p>
               <p>"Oh! this is not the lad," and let me go, but took hold of me again.</p>
